_text = "I could feel the electricity running through the air. The rain was pounding down on our umbrella while we gazed around at the scene before us.\n\nEvery couple of seconds a flash of lighting would light up the field. Immediately after, a boom would echo out around us. The storm was right above us, hovering like a massive beast climbing its way down from the clouds.\n\nI was about 10 years old at the time. My sense of fear was non existent. I wasn't afraid of the storm, that was before me. Looking back I wish I still had that courage."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, JeepMemory, JeepMemory, false)
